{"tid":1690112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角行人過路處地面 疑寫上警員個人資料","createTime":"2019-11-03T07:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T07:54:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6a870bc0cf4e104375f1048af4d89a5f7bd29c66","tid":1690112,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"再有示威者懷疑將警員資料寫於公眾地方。旺角亞皆老街與彌敦道交界，惠豐中心對著匯豐銀行的行人過路處，地面黃色油漆上遭示威者寫滿字句，當中包括陳姓、許姓及錢姓懷疑警員的個人資料，包括姓名、編號、身分證號碼、手機號碼及住址。<br />\n<br />\n而惠豐中心對開一個懷疑早前受示威者破壞的電箱表面，昨日凌晨被發現遭寫上相信是負責操作水炮車警員的個人資料。防暴警到場以天拿水抹走資料。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1627974/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%8E%E8%B7%AF%E8%99%95%E5%9C%B0%E9%9D%A2-%E7%96%91%E5%AF%AB%E4%B8%8A%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ObJjr1FTOX9.mRgf8SKFJQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUxMg--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/EqtRCBDpL4Q5Z3W1h5HhsA--~B/aD02MDA7dz03NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191103a142742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FObJjr1FTOX9.mRgf8SKFJQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUxMg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FEqtRCBDpL4Q5Z3W1h5HhsA--~B%2FaD02MDA7dz03NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191103a142742.jpg&h=2c2609cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8a7112dfe20f9e12d07a660061d2a72ee31ec47","tid":1690112,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:13:41.000Z","msg":"［行動］高人指點打破困局方法：火燒後欄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689276</a><br />\n<br />\n大家除咗上網鬧甴近平，仲有好多嘢可以做，為運動爭取勝利。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"abe994e16973d316e355408a6a7a316925800d41","tid":1690112,"uid":327943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:14:06.000Z","msg":"我建議佢哋落禁制令<br />\n禁止市民走上馬路以避免泄露警方私隱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016bcef08e8c14e364432c07941a1c639a353445","tid":1690112,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"星島同東方記者幫手fact check"},{"pid":"c18a815d5622cecba1236661fdcc1bfb0198dc67","tid":1690112,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"016bcef08e8c14e364432c07941a1c639a353445","tid":1690112,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"星島同東方記者幫手fact check"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:34:51.000Z","msg":"尋日行過旺角 好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5eda20ebb67a02174451496353ff60df9b4326","tid":1690112,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:54:24.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好周圍寫<br />\n尤其是啲柱啊牆啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw發夢中後排可唔可以click入黎睇睇 thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到黎可唔可以緊張少少 審時度勢..<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}